---

### 3.2 `services/import-workers` (Async Jobs)

Background workers for async and heavy tasks.

Responsibilities:
- Supplier catalog import
- Stock sync
- Price sync
- Invoice generation
- Email sending

Structure:

import-workers/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ src/
в”‚ в”њв”Ђв”Ђ jobs/
в”‚ в”њв”Ђв”Ђ common/
в”‚ в””в”Ђв”Ђ main.ts

Rules:
- No public APIs
- Triggered via queues or admin actions
- Uses same database as commerce-core
- Does not serve frontend traffic

